{{vgname|漫長等待|en=The Longing}}是由德國工作室Studio Seufz開發並由Application Systems Heidelberg發行在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和[[Linux|Linux]]平台上的[[點擊式冒險遊戲|點擊式冒險遊戲]]，於2020年3月5日公開發售。故事根據{{link-en|屈夫霍伊瑟山|Kyffhäuser|屈夫霍伊瑟山傳說}}改編，並圍繞著居住在地下王國的居民「一個影子」（Shade）發生，他需要在400天後喚醒熟睡的國王，在此期間，他必須找出消磨時光的辦法。

《漫長等待》的特點在於無論是否開啟，遊戲的400天皆與現實時間相等，且不能通過修改器更改電腦時間等方式加快進度。此實驗性質的做法也使得該作獲得評論家的廣泛讚賞，更因此獲得2020年[[獨立遊戲節|獨立遊戲節]]創新獎的提名。

== 遊戲玩法與故事 ==
[[File:TheLongingVideoGame_ShadeHome.png|thumb]]
《漫長等待》的劇情圍繞著「一個影子」（Shade）發生，他受命在400天後喚醒國王，值得注意的是，該400天與現實時間相若<ref name="One way" />。「一個影子」的行走速度極慢，不能奔跑<ref name="cunning">{{Cite web|last=Cunningham|first=James|date=2020-03-06|title=The Longing Completes its Yearning for Release|url=https://hardcoregamer.com/2020/03/05/the-longing-completes-its-yearning-for-release/368907/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615170720/https://hardcoregamer.com/2020/03/05/the-longing-completes-its-yearning-for-release/368907/|archive-date=2020-06-15|access-date=2020-05-03|website=Hardcore Gamer|language=en-US}}</ref>。玩家可以在《漫長等待》中探索洞穴，收集用來裝飾「一個影子」的房間的資源，以及做其他消磨時間的活動，例如閱讀{{Efn|可以閱讀的文章大多是經[[古騰堡計劃|古騰堡計劃]]得來的文學作品，例如[[赫爾曼·梅爾維爾|赫爾曼·梅爾維爾]]的《[[白鯨記|白鯨記]]》和[[弗里德里希·尼采|弗里德里希·尼采]]的《[[查拉圖斯特拉如是說|查拉圖斯特拉如是說]]》<ref name="design">{{Cite web|title=Designing the end of all Longing|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2020-02-27-designing-the-end-of-all-longing|first=Rebekah|last=Valentine|date=2020-02-27|website=GamesIndustry.biz|language=en|access-date=2020-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324080004/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2020-02-27-designing-the-end-of-all-longing|archive-date=March 24, 2020}}</ref>。|name=|group=}}或繪畫<ref name="WaPo" />。遊戲中許多地貌都會隨時間而變，舉例來說某些路障需要玩家等待一段時間才會出現<ref name="One way" />。《漫長等待》還有自動翻頁和標記地點等功能<ref>{{Cite web|last=Gregoire|first=Jesee|date=2020-03-05|title=The Longing Review - Jump Dash Roll|url=https://www.jumpdashroll.com/article/the-longing-review|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615170851/https://www.jumpdashroll.com/article/the-longing-review|archive-date=2020-06-15|access-date=2020-05-06|website=JumpDashRoll}}</ref>，玩家也可以指示「一個影子」走到前次存檔的位置、返回家中或隨機漫步<ref name="Encourages" /><ref name="4p" />。

玩家的主要目標會在待辦清單上顯示，而大多數目標完成後會改善「一個影子」的生活<ref>{{Cite web|title=The deep darkness of caves and mushrooms in The Longing|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2020/03/12/the-deep-darkness-of-caves-and-mushrooms-in-the-longing/|last=Bell|first=Alice|date=2020-03-12|website=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|language=en-US|access-date=2020-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412225748/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2020/03/12/the-deep-darkness-of-caves-and-mushrooms-in-the-longing/|archive-date=April 12, 2020}}</ref>。玩家不用與《漫長等待》的世界作出任何交互以加快時間，因為無論採取哪一種行動，或是否開啟遊戲也好，計時器都會照正常速度運行{{Efn|唯一例外是「永恆地牢」，當玩家身處在該地方時時計器會停止<ref name="cunning" /><ref name="design" />。|name=|group=}}<ref name="Gloomy">{{Cite web|last=Hadley|first=Jupiter|date=2019-11-25|title='The Longing' Explores Gloomy Depths Over 400 Real-World Days|url=https://indiegamesplus.com/2019/11/the-longing-explores-gloomy-depths-over-400-real-world-days|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615171022/https://indiegamesplus.com/2019/11/the-longing-explores-gloomy-depths-over-400-real-world-days|archive-date=2020-06-15|access-date=2020-05-01|website=Indie Games Plus|language=en-US}}</ref>。加快計時器的辦法包括讓「一個影子」身處在其裝潢過的房間內，房間越多裝飾，計時器便會加速得越快，其餘例如繪畫和閱讀等也可做到同樣效果<ref name="Encourages">{{Cite web|title=The Longing, Which Can Take Over A Year To Finish, Encourages You To Embrace Waiting|url=https://kotaku.com/the-longing-which-can-take-over-a-year-to-finish-enco-1842213852|last=MacLeod|first=Riley|date=2020-03-09|website=Kotaku|language=en-us|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325150225/https://kotaku.com/the-longing-which-can-take-over-a-year-to-finish-enco-1842213852|archive-date=March 25, 2020|access-date=2020-05-01}}</ref>。在計時器不斷運行下，玩家可以通過只開啟一次遊戲，等待400天後重開的情況通關，但這不是Studio Seufz預期玩家遊玩的方式<ref name="One way">{{Cite web|title=One Way To Beat This Upcoming Puzzle Game Is To Wait 400 Days|url=https://kotaku.com/one-way-to-beat-this-upcoming-puzzle-game-is-to-wait-40-1840513881|last=Jackson|first=Gita|date=2020-12-18|website=Kotaku|language=en-us|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306204143/https://kotaku.com/one-way-to-beat-this-upcoming-puzzle-game-is-to-wait-40-1840513881|archive-date=March 6, 2020|access-date=2020-05-01}}</ref>。為了預防[[電子遊戲作弊|作弊]]，《漫長等待》設計了一個「永恆地牢」，若玩家通過修改器更改[[系統時間|系統時間]]就會被關進那裡，並需要點擊畫面400次才可離開<ref name="One way" />。遊戲包含四個結局，但不是全部都需要玩家等待計時器歸零<ref name="Encourages" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=I have finished the sad tamogotchi game that is The Longing|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2020/04/02/i-have-finished-the-sad-tamogotchi-game-that-is-the-longing/|last=Bell|first=Alice|date=2020-04-02|website=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|language=en-US|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519072943/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2020/04/02/i-have-finished-the-sad-tamogotchi-game-that-is-the-longing/|archive-date=May 19, 2020}}</ref>。

== 開發與發行 ==
《漫長等待》的故事靈感來自{{link-en|屈夫霍伊瑟山|Kyffhäuser|屈夫霍伊瑟山傳說}}，特別參考了{{link-en|弗里德里希·呂克特|Friedrich Rückert}}的詩作《屈夫霍伊瑟山脈的紅鬍子》（''Kyffhäuser Mountains Barbarossa''），其[[矮人_(中土大陸)|矮人]]主角每100年就要檢查一次國王是否準備醒來。遊戲總監安塞爾姆·派塔（Anselm Pyta）對該詩很感興趣，並希望改編後的遊戲專注在角色及其心理狀態上<ref name="One way" />。也因如此，《漫長等待》的大部分內容都圍繞「孤獨」這一主題上<ref name="roadto">{{Cite web|last=Couture|first=Joel|date=2020-02-18|title=Road to the IGF: Studio Seufz's THE LONGING|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/358061/Road_to_the_IGF_Studio_Seufzs_THE_LONGING.php|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414180758/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/358061/Road_to_the_IGF_Studio_Seufzs_THE_LONGING.php|archive-date=April 14, 2020|access-date=2020-06-14|website=Gamasutra|language=en}}</ref>。遊戲玩法還受到諸如《{{link-en|點擊英雄|Clicker Heroes}}》等[[獨立遊戲|獨立遊戲]]啟發<ref name="One way" />。在發行前，《漫長等待》曾在AdventureX 2020上進行演示<ref name="Gloomy" />。2020年3月5日，遊戲正式在[[Steam|Steam]]（[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows]]、[[MacOS|Mac]]和[[Linux|Linux]]）上公開發售<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pass 400 days underground in IGF-nominee The Longing, coming to Steam on March 5 (Win/Mac/Linux review copies available now)|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/356639/Pass_400_days_underground_in_IGFnominee_The_Longing_coming_to_Steam_on_March_5_WinMacLinux_review_copies_available_now.php|access-date=2020-06-14|website=Gamasutra|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114162135/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/356639/Pass_400_days_underground_in_IGFnominee_The_Longing_coming_to_Steam_on_March_5_WinMacLinux_review_copies_available_now.php|archive-date=January 14, 2020}}</ref>。

