《漫長等待》在發行後獲得廣泛讚譽，評論家尤其讚賞Studio Seufz的實驗精神。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，其根據6條評價獲得76/100分<ref name="metacritic" />。

《[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]》的喬金·基爾曼（Joakim Kilman）給予《漫長等待》82/100分，稱其是「迷人有趣的實驗性遊戲」<ref name="pcsweden">{{Cite web|last=Kilman|first=Joakim|date=2020-03-05|title=The Longing – Recension|trans-title=The Longing – Review|url=https://www.pcgamer.se/2020/03/the-longing-recension/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615171132/https://www.pcgamer.se/2020/03/the-longing-recension/|archive-date=2020-06-15|access-date=2020-05-01|website=Svenska PC Gamer|language=sv}}</ref>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的克里斯托弗·伯德（Christopher Byrd） 為《漫長等待》給出90/100分，他表示其創造力水平重新激發了其對遊戲的期待，並拿該作與《[[見證者|見證者]]》以及《{{link-en|新手指南|The Beginner's Guide}}》等作進行比較<ref name="WaPo">{{Cite web|title=Review {{!}} 'The Longing': Patience (and lots of it) is required, but it's worth every minute|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/video-games/reviews/longing-patience-lots-it-is-required-its-worth-every-minute/|last=Byrd|first=Christopher|date=2020-03-05|website=Washington Post|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411222359/https://www.washingtonpost.com/video-games/reviews/longing-patience-lots-it-is-required-its-worth-every-minute/|archive-date=April 11, 2020|access-date=2020-05-01}}</ref>。因著《漫長等待》的發行日期，《[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar]]》的蕾切兒·韋伯（Rachel Weber）稱該作概括了「在[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2020年大流行]]底下生活的人們」<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Longing is the indie game that sums up self-solation perfectly|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/the-longing-is-the-indie-game-that-sums-up-self-solation-perfectly/|last=Weber|first=Rachel|date=2020-04-03|website=GamesRadar|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406034220/https://www.gamesradar.com/the-longing-is-the-indie-game-that-sums-up-self-solation-perfectly/|archive-date=April 6, 2020|access-date=2020-05-01}}</ref>。

一些評論家亦批評《漫長等待》缺乏內容，《{{link-en|The Games Machine|The Games Machine}}》的費羅納托·埃馬努埃萊（Feronato Emaneule）雖然稱讚其故事，但同時也指出該作缺少謎題和過多停頓<ref>{{Cite web|last=Emanuele|first=Feronato|date=2020-05-03|title=The Longing – Recensione|url=https://www.thegamesmachine.it/the-longing-pc/the-longing-recensione/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411185502/https://www.thegamesmachine.it/the-longing-pc/the-longing-recensione/|archive-date=April 11, 2020|access-date=2020-06-14|website=The Games Machine|language=it}}</ref>。而《Cubed3》的阿薩納西奧斯·阿拉沃西塔斯（Athanasios Aravositas）則埋怨道難以在遊玩《漫長等待》時沉醉在其內容之中<ref>{{Cite web|last=Aravositas|first=Athanasios|date=2020-03-24|title=THE LONGING (PC) Review|url=http://www.cubed3.com/review/5840/1/the-longing-pc.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411185513/http://www.cubed3.com/review/5840/1/the-longing-pc.html|archive-date=April 11, 2020|access-date=2020-06-14|website=Cubed3}}</ref>。

